From gregl Greg Lewis Subject Re please read In article Brian LaRose writes This just a warning to EVERYBODY on the Watch out for folks standing NEXT to the road or on They can cause SERIOUS HARM to you and your just a cliff notes version of my story follows last night I was travelling on the interstate here in knoxville I was taking an offramp exit to another interstate and my wife suddenly screamed and something LARGE hit the side of my We slowed down but after looking back to see the vandals standing there we drove on to the police She did get a good look at the guy and saw him cock his arm with something the size of a cinderblock BUT I never saw We are VERY lucky the truck sits up high on the road if it would have hit her window it would have killed The police are looking for the guy but in all likelyhood he is Stuff I am sorry to report that in Southern California it was a sick sport for a while to drop concrete blocks from the overpasses onto the Several persons were killed when said blocks came through their Many overpass bridges are now fenced and they have made it illegal to loiter on such bridges as if that would stop such people Yet many bridges are NOT I always look up at a bridge while I still have time to take evasive action even though this sport has not reached us here in Greg L Photojournalism sequence Department of Journalism CSU Fresno Fresno CA